{"tid":2058566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教大學生會掛「獨立」橫額 校方：不支持港獨促移除","createTime":"2020-06-10T09:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T09:33:46.000Z","uid":70063,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3b4bc1288e2d3b90f84eb307c99da93011933980","tid":2058566,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:18:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%95%99%e8%82%b2/article/20200605/s00011/1591296643665/%e6%95%99%e5%a4%a7%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e6%9c%83%e6%8e%9b%e3%80%8c%e7%8d%a8%e7%ab%8b%e3%80%8d%e6%a9%ab%e9%a1%8d-%e6%a0%a1%e6%96%b9-%e4%b8%8d%e6%94%af%e6%8c%81%e6%b8%af%e7%8d%a8%e4%bf%83%e7%a7%bb%e9%99%a4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20200605%2Fs00011%2F1591296643665%2F%25e6%2595%2599%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%2594%259f%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%258e%259b%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%258d%25a8%25e7%25ab%258b%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%25a9%25ab%25e9%25a1%258d-%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e6%2596%25b9-%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%2594%25af%25e6%258c%2581%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%258d%25a8%25e4%25bf%2583%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e9%2599%25a4&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa2Ckd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=cc5ffc58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20200605%2Fs00011%2F1591296643665%2F%25e6%2595%2599%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%2594%259f%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%258e%259b%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%258d%25a8%25e7%25ab%258b%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%25a9%25ab%25e9%25a1%258d-%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e6%2596%25b9-%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%2594%25af%25e6%258c%2581%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%258d%25a8%25e4%25bf%2583%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e9%2599%25a4&h=a93eb952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%95%99%e8%82%b2/article/20200605/s00011/1591296643665/%e6%95%99%e5%a4%a7%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e6%9c%83%e6%8e%9b%e3%80%8c%e7%8d%a8%e7%ab%8b%e3%80%8d%e6%a9%ab%e9%a1%8d-%e6%a0%a1%e6%96%b9-%e4%b8%8d%e6%94%af%e6%8c%81%e6%b8%af%e7%8d%a8%e4%bf%83%e7%a7%bb%e9%99%a4</a><br />\n<br />\n教育大學學生會臨時行政委員會（臨委會）六四前夕於學校中央廣場，掛起分別印有「INDEPENDENCE」（獨立）、「HONG KONG」、「光復香港 時代革命」3幅橫額，惟臨委會稱橫額昨日遭人𠝹破。<br />\n<br />\n教育大學回應，校長2017年發表聯署聲明，表明不支持「港獨」主張，認為這違反《基本法》；校方前晚向學生會發出電郵，表達遺憾及重申大學立場，已要求學生會盡快移除橫額。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不足1日遭𠝹破 臨委會譴責禁言</strong><br />\n<br />\n臨委會周三於校內掛3幅黑底白字橫額，稱「堅持以探討香港前途為宗旨，守護討論香港前途的空間，捍衛港人自決之權利和意志」，未夠24小時，臨委會上傳照片稱橫額遭人破壞，照片可見被𠝹破。<br />\n<br />\n臨委會其後發聲明強烈譴責破壞與噤聲行為，「亦永不會棄歷史如敝屣或甘於落得自我噤聲，更不會放棄捍衛港人自決之權利和意志之立場」；又指大學為學術自由及擁有言論自由的文明地方，任何人不得因自己所思所想而禁止他人言論。"},{"pid":"73e6c864a79cf689e02ee8d23507fc16efef9ad1","tid":2058566,"uid":4285,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n獨立呢個concept,真係多謝廢老689 炒熱"},{"pid":"c5d9e393188f876d6e5ec61d722530a4f0194e2f","tid":2058566,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:23:30.000Z","msg":"是旦啦你鐘意點界就點界<br />\n香港獨立唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acf924a12c922dba26d8b59c2e93380056ac351","tid":2058566,"uid":110509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"掛<br />\n支持<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">獨立</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">關稅區</span> 會點"},{"pid":"b02f20ae1a6f40ab7398db4144105706780a0341","tid":2058566,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"好地地比真普選 今日可能個個都我係中國人啊hi"},{"pid":"2805597152dccefa9124129f9bc251f878525dd5","tid":2058566,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c13e559fb89dd7e0fa632e3cd47974e29ae734","tid":2058566,"uid":12119